title: Logan Paul Says Ethan Is Scum Of The Internet - H3 After Dark #21
description: On this episode of H3 After Dark the foot soldiers of the H3 army go to WAR!!! We take a trip down memory lane and see who the real scum of the internet is... We also have plenty of goofs and gaffs along the way- something is about to BUST!
